			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				The skeletons in Rathe Mountains are not greater<BR>
skeletons, they are giant skeletons.  It is a <BR>
fairly common drop, levels are like 24 to 27.<BR>
To answer somone elses question, the bloodblack<BR>
wand does absoluty nothing, it is just for the<BR>
quest.  At level 22 I was able to take the <BR>
skeletons with a level 25 tank, or a level 25 <BR>
druid with me.  Good exp and fair loot, but <BR>
dangerous zone at level 22.  That is all I know<BR>
about the quest for now.<BR>

